OL,3,CHolyrood election Scotland's chance to
OL,4,Cvote 'no confidence' in Starmer ` Flynn
OL,6,FThe Holyrood election is "Scotland's
OL,7,Fopportunity to vote 'no confidence' in
OL,8,FKeir Starmer", the SNP's Westminster
OL,9,Fleader has said.
OL,11,FStephen Flynn said the May 7 election
OL,12,Fis the country's chance to secure a
OL,13,F"fresh start with independence" and
OL,14,Fescape the "constant chaos of
OL,15,FWestminster control".
OL,26,@nD@ZOUpD@MO]uD@AOUuD@_O]vD@LOUwD@TO]
