OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777172625
OL,3,CHolyrood election Scotland's chance to
OL,4,Cvote 'no confidence' in Starmer ` Flynn
OL,6,FMr Flynn said it is a "disgrace" that
OL,7,Fthe UK Government is "completely
OL,8,Fconsumed by the Peter Mandelson
OL,9,Fscandal and distracted from the issues
OL,10,Fthat matter to voters" amid the cost-
OL,11,Fof-living crisis.
OL,13,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,14,Ffaced calls to resign amid the fallout
OL,15,Ffrom the Lord Peter Mandelson vetting
OL,16,Fscandal which was sparked after it
OL,17,Femerged he had not passed vetting
OL,18,Fchecks but had still been appointed
OL,19,FBritish ambassador to the US.
OL,26,@nD@WOUnD@`O]oD@VOUrD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
