OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777172625
OL,3,CHolyrood election Scotland's chance to
OL,4,Cvote 'no confidence' in Starmer ` Flynn
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister fired Foreign
OL,7,FOffice chief Sir Olly Robbins over the
OL,8,Fissue and has said he has been
OL,9,Fexonerated over accusations he misled
OL,10,FMPs by evidence from Sir Olly.
OL,12,FMr Flynn said: "The election on 7th
OL,13,FMay is Scotland's opportunity to vote
OL,14,F'no confidence' in Keir Starmer and
OL,15,Fsecure a fresh start with independence.
OL,26,@tD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777172625
OL,3,CHolyrood election Scotland's chance to
OL,4,Cvote 'no confidence' in Starmer ` Flynn
OL,6,F"If Labour MPs won't do the decent
OL,7,Fthing, and bring forward a vote of no
OL,8,Fconfidence themselves, Scottish voters
OL,9,Fcan take action on 7th May ` by voting
OL,10,FSNP to sack Keir Starmer and escape
OL,11,Fthe constant chaos of Westminster
OL,12,Fcontrol.
OL,14,F"It is a disgrace that, at a time when
OL,15,Ffamilies need a government that is
OL,16,Ffully focused on tackling the cost-of-
OL,17,Fliving emergency, the Labour
OL,18,Fgovernment is completely consumed by
OL,19,Fthe Peter Mandelson scandal and
OL,20,Fdistracted from the issues that matter
OL,21,Fto voters.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
