CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777172625
OL,3,CHolyrood election Scotland's chance to
OL,4,Cvote 'no confidence' in Starmer ` Flynn
OL,6,F"While John Swinney's SNP government
OL,7,Fis laser-focused on helping families `
OL,8,FKeir Starmer is only interested in
OL,9,Fsaving his own skin and hasn't lifted
OL,10,Fa finger to help households with the
OL,11,Fsoaring cost of living under the
OL,12,FLabour Party."
OL,14,FLord Mandelson was sacked last year,
OL,15,Fless than a year into the job, after
OL,16,Fdetails of his association with the
OL,17,Fpaedophile financier Jeffrey Epstein
OL,18,Femerged in files published by the US
OL,19,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@NO]
