OL,3,CHolyrood election Scotland's chance to
OL,4,Cvote 'no confidence' in Starmer ` Flynn
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister has been under
OL,7,Fpressure over the vetting issue in
OL,8,Frecent days.
OL,10,FMr Flynn said: "Keir Starmer is doing
OL,11,Fmore damage with every day that he
OL,12,Fclings on to power.
OL,14,F"His position is completely untenable
OL,15,Fand Labour MPs are doing voters a
OL,16,Fdisservice by keeping him in place.
OL,26,@rD@POUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
