OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777172625
OL,3,CHolyrood election Scotland's chance to
OL,4,Cvote 'no confidence' in Starmer ` Flynn
OL,6,F"The election is the key moment that
OL,7,Fcan seal Keir Starmer's fate. On 7th
OL,8,FMay, people in Scotland can vote SNP
OL,9,Fto show Keir Starmer the door and
OL,10,Fsecure that fresh start of
OL,11,Findependence."
OL,13,FScottish Labour deputy leader Jackie
OL,14,FBaillie said "The SNP's endless
OL,15,Fattempts to deflect attention from its
OL,16,Fown shameful record in government is
OL,17,Fgetting embarrassing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@NO]vD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
