PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777172625
OL,3,CHolyrood election Scotland's chance to
OL,4,Cvote 'no confidence' in Starmer ` Flynn
OL,6,F"This election is about Scotland's
OL,7,Fgovernment, our NHS, our schools, our
OL,8,Flocal services, our community safety
OL,9,Fand our transport system ` but Stephen
OL,10,FFlynn seems to think these issues
OL,11,Fdon't matter.
OL,13,F"Anas Sarwar has been clear that a
OL,14,Fvote for Scottish Labour in this
OL,15,Felection is not an endorsement of Keir
OL,16,FStarmer ` it is a vote to change the
OL,17,Fgovernment here in Scotland.
OL,19,F"The SNP is letting Scotland down but
OL,20,Fonly Scottish Labour can beat them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
