SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777172625
OL,3,CHolyrood election Scotland's chance to
OL,4,Cvote 'no confidence' in Starmer ` Flynn
OL,6,F"The choice on the ballot on May 7 is
OL,7,Fbetween more of the same with John
OL,8,FSwinney and the SNP and change with
OL,9,FAnas Sarwar and Scottish Labour.
OL,11,F"A Scottish Labour government will fix
OL,12,Fthe mess, get the basics right and
OL,13,Fdeliver a better future for Scotland."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@fO]
